title: Add devmove consensus engine to smoke tests
Add dockerfile to publish sdk to npm
Add license as pointed by the Fossology scan
body:
Fossology scan details can be found in STL-398

Signed-off-by: kulkarniamol <amol.kulkarni@intel.com>

title: Update gpg key used by apt to the correct one
Add SDK files from core repo
body:
This PR pulls the Javascript SDK files from the core repo , adding them here. This will simplify build processes and the development workflow. In addition to pulling the original files and commits, a number of additional commits rearrange/rename the files and incorporate integration tests.

Note that this is a very large PR with thousands of commits, only the last fifteen of which are original. It is probably simpler to review the [source branch](https://github.com/Cargill/sawtooth-sdk-javascript/tree/c001-add-core-js-sdk) as a final product, then to go commit by commit here.

The sister PR to this one is [Remove JS SDK files from core repo](https://github.com/hyperledger/sawtooth-core/pull/1730) on `hyperledger/sawtooth-core`.
